<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">سمع:</span> أبا مَحْذُورة الجُمَحِيَّ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى عنه:</span> ابنه عثمان.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روي له:</span> أبو داود، والنَّسائي.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
